---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="DMCA & Copyright Policy — Rift Wars" description="DMCA copyright policy and intellectual property protection for Rift Wars.">
  <section class="section-padding pt-32 bg-mm-bg">
    <div class="section-container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-orbitron text-3xl font-bold text-mm-text mb-8 neon-text">DMCA & Copyright Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Meta Machina Studio LLC</strong> respects intellectual property rights and responds to valid
          DMCA takedown notices in accordance with the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (17 U.S.C. &sect; 512).
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">Our Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Meta Machina Studio LLC owns all rights to the Meta Machina name, logo, branding, Rift Wars game content,
          card art, character designs, lore, music, code, and UI design. Unauthorized commercial use of our
          intellectual property is strictly prohibited.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">Filing a DMCA Complaint</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          If you believe your copyrighted work has been infringed, send a written notice to our designated agent
          containing:
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Identification of the copyrighted work you claim has been infringed</li>
          <li>Identification of the material you claim is infringing, with sufficient detail to locate it</li>
          <li>Your contact information (name, address, telephone, email)</li>
          <li>A statement that you have a good faith belief the use is not authorized by the copyright owner</li>
          <li>A statement under penalty of perjury that the information in your notice is accurate and that you are the copyright owner or authorized to act on their behalf</li>
          <li>Your physical or electronic signature</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">Response Timeline</h2>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>We will acknowledge receipt within 24-48 hours</li>
          <li>Valid claims are reviewed within 1-3 business days</li>
          <li>Obvious violations (commercial use of our trademarks, wholesale theft of creative materials) may result in immediate removal</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">Counter-Notification</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          If you believe content was removed in error, you may file a counter-notification containing your signature,
          identification of the removed material, a statement under penalty of perjury that the removal was a mistake,
          and your consent to jurisdiction in Clark County, Nevada.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">Repeat Infringers</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          We enforce a three-strike policy: first offense results in a warning, second in temporary suspension,
          and third in permanent account termination. Serious violations (commercial IP theft) may warrant
          immediate termination.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">False Claims</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Filing a false DMCA notice may result in liability under Section 512(f) of the DMCA, including damages,
          attorney fees, and potential law enforcement referral.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">Designated Agent</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Meta Machina Studio LLC<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@metamachina.io" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">legal@metamachina.io</a><br />
          Registered Agent: Registered Agents Inc., 732 S 6th ST, STE R, Las Vegas, NV 89101
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
